<br>
He's a nice guy (girl? - he's never really said), with a strange sense of humor and style, both in-game and RL (have him show you pictures of his house and odds and ends collections ... it's wierd, to say the least). I don't have a problem with what he does, he certainly makes no bones about it or pretends it's something else. I've chatted with Worry quite a few times, mostly months ago on SZ. I don't dislike him, just I don't expect anything he does to be beneficial to anyone but him. If it helps someone else out, that's accidental but not all bad.<br>
<br>
But don't mistake it. EQ is a business for Worry, not a game. There's a very big difference, and forgetting that warps your perspective of the whole situation. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;font-family:courier;font-size:small;">&quot;It never stops hurting, you just go faster...&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> - <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Greg LeMond</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gyorg@graffeswizardcompilation>Gyorg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 128<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/25/03 1:35:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26263.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> PBAE?</span><hr size=1> Are they leading the swarm of mobs around when they do this? If so it seems like the song they are using can't be a PBAE, since 'point blank' means the mobs are right next to you. Unless they have a larger radius than our PBAE nukes. Or unless they are standing still and twisting some kind of stun song. But it doesnt make sense that they would be able to nuke an unlimited number of mobs, from a distance, while running. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lordbug>LordBug</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/g